# Vercel KV (Redis) - automatically set when you create a KV database in Vercel
# No manual setup needed! Just create a KV database in your Vercel project:
# 1. Go to your Vercel project
# 2. Click "Storage" tab
# 3. Click "Create Database" -> "KV (Redis)"
# 4. Name it "countdown-sync"
# 5. Click "Create"
# The environment variables will be automatically added to your project!
